sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as Developer
    participant CLI as Eleventy CLI
    participant Config as .eleventy.js
    participant Logger as Custom Logger
    participant Plugins as Plugins Module
    participant Filters as Filters Module
    participant Shortcodes as Shortcodes Module
    participant Collections as Collections Module
    participant Airtable as Airtable CMS
    participant Templates as Nunjucks Templates
    participant Output as _site Directory

    Note over User,Output: Build Initialization

    User->>CLI: npm run build
    CLI->>+Config: Initialize configuration
    
    Config->>+Logger: Start initialization group
    Logger->>Logger: Log initialization message
    
    Note over Config,Output: Passthrough Copy Configuration
    
    Config->>Config: Configure passthrough copy
    Note right of Config: robots.txt<br/>assets folder<br/>js to assets/js<br/>video files
    
    Config->>Config: Set server watch options
    Note right of Config: Watch _site CSS files
    
    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
    Note over Config,Shortcodes: Register 11ty Components
    
    Config->>+Plugins: Register plugins
    Plugins->>Plugins: Load eleventy-navigation
    Plugins->>Plugins: Load eleventy-img
    Plugins->>Plugins: Load other plugins
    Plugins->>-Config: Plugins registered
    
    Config->>+Filters: Register template filters
    Filters->>Filters: Load custom filters
    Filters->>Filters: Load date filters
    Filters->>Filters: Load utility filters
    Filters->>-Config: Filters registered
    
    Config->>+Shortcodes: Register shortcodes
    Shortcodes->>Shortcodes: Load custom shortcodes
    Shortcodes->>Shortcodes: Load image shortcodes
    Shortcodes->>-Config: Shortcodes registered
    end
    
    rect rgb(255, 240, 230)
    Note over Config,Airtable: Data Collection from CMS
    
    Config->>+Collections: Register collections
    Collections->>Collections: Read site.json config
    
    loop For each Airtable table
        Collections->>+Airtable: Fetch table data
        Note right of Airtable: tableName<br/>tableView<br/>cache duration
        Airtable->>Airtable: Query records
        Airtable->>Airtable: Apply view filters
        Airtable->>-Collections: Return records
        Collections->>Collections: Create 11ty collection
    end
    
    Collections->>-Config: Collections ready
    end
    
    Config->>-Logger: Log completion
    Logger->>Logger: Success message
    
    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
    Note over CLI,Output: Template Processing
    
    CLI->>CLI: Scan input directory
    Note right of CLI: njk/_pages
    
    loop For each template file
        CLI->>+Templates: Process template
        Templates->>Templates: Load frontmatter
        Templates->>Templates: Apply filters
        Templates->>Templates: Execute shortcodes
        Templates->>Templates: Access collections data
        Templates->>Templates: Render Nunjucks
        Templates->>-CLI: Compiled HTML
        
        CLI->>+Output: Write HTML file
        Output->>-CLI: File written
    end
    end
    
    CLI->>User: Build complete
    
    Note over User,Output: Output Structure
    Note right of Output: index.html<br/>about/index.html<br/>projects/index.html<br/>assets/styles.css<br/>assets/js/<br/>assets/video/